Package: arasul-platform
Version: 1.0.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: docker.io (>= 20.10), docker-compose (>= 1.29), python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, curl, avahi-daemon, avahi-utils, libnss-mdns, postgresql-client
Maintainer: Arasul Platform <support@arasul.local>
Description: Arasul Edge AI Platform
 A complete Edge AI appliance for NVIDIA Jetson AGX Orin.
 Includes AI services (LLM, Embeddings), workflow automation (n8n),
 object storage (MinIO), and comprehensive monitoring with self-healing capabilities.
 .
 This package installs all necessary components and configures the system
 for autonomous operation with minimal user intervention.
Homepage: https://github.com/arasul/platform
